13, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919689344, \"rank\": 4.1390185816417404e-09, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States was behind for most of the game and held the lead for less than three and a half minutes in the crucial fourth quarter to secure a spot in the gold medal game on Saturday, August 10 (Sunday, August 11) against hosts France.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919689344, \"rank\": 4.1390185816417404e-09, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was a godlike performance,\\\" Kevin Durant, a forward for the NBA's Phoenix Suns who had nine points against Serbia, said of Curry.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.063174227257336e-16, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999051852, \"rank\": 6.794320508140203e-11, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1094, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999924019470998, \"rank\": 5.975537812311371e-06, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Steph, he felt like he was struggling throughout the whole tournament and tonight, he showed up.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"God was with him tonight.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was with us tonight and through Steph.\\\"\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"score\": 0.8233690901270779, \"rank\": 0.21409776317707635, \"text\": \"Steph\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Durant described it as one of the best games he had ever seen Curry play, the four-time NBA champion with the Golden State Warriors shrugged off his personal contribution to the victory, saying his performance was merely what the game called for.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3451879326761962e-12, \"text\": \"NBA champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have not had many opportunities and have not shot the ball well the whole tournament,\\\" said the 36-year-old.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But it does not waver your confidence to meet the moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You live for those moments and does not matter if you shoot three times or however many I shot tonight.\\\"\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Curry, who sank 9 of 14 three-point shots on Thursday, said the United States would need to dominate early in the final against France for a chance at gold.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999919689344, \"rank\": 4.1390185816417404e-09, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8855657184189052, \"rank\": 0.12921003757485086, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know they are going to feed off their home energy,\\\" Curry said of France, who beat Germany 73-69 earlier on Thursday to reach the final.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2047, \"end\": 2053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8855657184189052, \"rank\": 0.12921003757485086, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2064, \"end\": 2071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res